/ Rails flash messages styled for Bootstrap 3.0
- flash.each do |name, msg|
  - if msg.is_a?(String)
    - alert_class = message_alert_class(name)
    = content_tag :div, id: "flash_#{name}", class: "alert alert-dismissable alert-#{alert_class} animated fadeInDown" do
      %button(type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true")<
        &times
      - if name == :notice
        = fa 'check'
      %strong<
        = msg
